The paper focuses on video question answering, which involves modeling visual and linguistic concepts and their relations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper introduces a reusable neural unit for representation and reasoning, which falls under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper specifically applies this architecture to video, indicating that it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
